    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Your construct eidolon is particularly easy to reconfigure, gaining an additional evolution that suits both of your whims. Choose one additional evolution feat of 6th level or lower. Your eidolon gains that feat. You can Retrain this feat for any other evolution feat of 6th level or lower with only a single day of downtime if you succeed at a <span data-pf2-check=\"crafting\" data-pf2-label=\"Reconfigured Evolution DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"@self.level\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Crafting</span> check, with a standard DC of your eidolon's level. If you fail, you can try again on a later day. Many summoners choose Eidolon's Wrath for this ability.</p>"
